---
title: "About"
description: "Learn more about the history and future of Electron Workshop"
layout: base.njk
permalink: "/about/"
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-8 offset-md-2">
      <div class="main-timeline">
        {% for card in timeline %}
        <a href="#" class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-icon"><i class="bi {{ card.icon }}"></i></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="title">{{ card.title }}</h3>
            <p class="description text-preline">{{ card.text }}</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 pt-3 border-top">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Initiatives</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-4">Ongoing programs run by and for the Electron Workshop community.</p>
        {% for item in initiatives %}
        <div class="mb-4">
          <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">
            <a href="/initiatives/{{ item.slug }}/">{{ item.title }}</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">{{ item.text }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
        <p class="small text-secondary">Interested in joining? Email <strong>network[at]electronworkshop.com.au</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 pt-3 border-top">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Chainferences</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-4">We run community satellite gatherings alongside major open-source and technology conferences across Australia.</p>
        {% for conf in chainferences %}
        <div class="mb-4">
          <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">
            <a href="/chainference/{{ conf.slug }}/">{{ conf.title }}</a>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">{{ conf.tagline }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

